data.description: Welcome to 2581 18th Ave N, a delightful residence boasting a cozy and functional split floor plan, perfect for modern living. This home offers an abundance of character and features such as hardwood floors, cedar wood closets, and original hallway nook. The charming bathroom showcases impeccably preserved original tiles, reflecting the unique character of this home.  The updated kitchen has a new stainless steel refrigerator and spacious kitchen bar and eat-in counter design.  The primary bedroom, can be transformed into a spacious retreat to fit any size bed.  Hosting gatherings is a delight in the expansive family room, creating a warm and inviting ambiance for cherished moments with loved ones.  Outdoor living is a pleasure with a generous fenced backyard that beckons you to bask in the Florida sun, offering an abundance of space for recreational activities and relaxation. Additionally, a convenient shed provides practical storage solutions.  The house is minutes away from I-275, downtown various shops such as Publix, Home Depot, Lowe’s, Mazzaro’s Italian Market and various restaurants.  Schedule your tour today!
